      "name": "Levia-Dragoon - Daedalus",
      "effect": "3 WATER monsters\nThis card's name becomes \"Umi\" while in the Monster Zone. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Levia-Dragoon - Daedalus\" once per turn. If this card is Link Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 monster that mentions \"Atlantis, the Dragon City\" from your Deck. During the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can send 1 face-up \"Umi\" you control to the GY; discard your opponent's entire hand, and if you do, they draw the same number of cards. Neither player can activate cards or effects in response to this effect's activation.",
      "official": false
    },
